pageContext.claim: [Gen. Qasem Soleimani was meeting with] “the head of Hezbollah”
pageContext.analysis: Before his death, Soleimani was met at Baghdad airport by Iraqi paramilitary leader Abu Mahdi al-Muhandis, the head of Kata'ib Hezbollah. That is a completely different group than the Lebanese militant group and political party, Hezbollah, led by Hassan Nasrallah.
